Valid weapon types

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=



Metal (use blacksmith or forge weapon)

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

long-sword      short-sword
bastard-sword   two-handed-sword
morning-star    dagger


Metal and wood (use blacksmith or forge weapon AND carpentry)

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=--=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

war-hammer         footman's-mace
footman's-flail    halberd
glaive


Carpentry

-=-=-=-=-

quarter-staff



Other types may come up soon, so keep watching!

